=head1 DESCRIPTION

Contains detailed information about a report setting.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Accounts => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

These are the accounts to be included in the report.

Use string value of C<ROOT> to include all organizational units.


=head2 FrameworkArns => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

The Amazon Resource Names (ARNs) of the frameworks a report covers.


=head2 NumberOfFrameworks => Int

The number of frameworks a report covers.


=head2 OrganizationUnits => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

These are the Organizational Units to be included in the report.


=head2 Regions => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

These are the Regions to be included in the report.

Use the wildcard as the string value to include all Regions.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> ReportTemplate => Str

Identifies the report template for the report. Reports are built using
a report template. The report templates are:

C<RESOURCE_COMPLIANCE_REPORT | CONTROL_COMPLIANCE_REPORT |
BACKUP_JOB_REPORT | COPY_JOB_REPORT | RESTORE_JOB_REPORT>



